data.name: CarouselPanelParameterSet
data.value: Gets or sets the collection of custom parameters that vary, according to a specific law.

data.name: CarouselPanelAnimationTime
data.value: Specifies the time taken by transition animations.

data.name: CarouselPanelSmoothingTimeFraction
data.value: For internal use.

data.name: CarouselPanelVisibleItemCount
data.value: Gets or sets the number of items that are visible to an end-user along a path at one time.This proeprty is not in effect when a path is specified via the CarouselPanel.PointPathFunction property.

data.name: CarouselPanelItemMovingPath
data.value: Gets or sets the path along which the Carousel's items are evenly arranged.

data.name: CarouselPanelOffsetDistributionFunction
data.value: Gets or sets the function that calculates the relative positions of the CarouselPanel's items along the path.

data.name: CarouselPanelOffsetAnimationAddFunction
data.value: Gets or sets the function whose values are added to the CarouselPanel.OffsetDistributionFunction function when calculating positions of an item during its animation (its movement from one position to another).

data.name: CarouselPanelPointPathFunction
data.value: Gets or sets a piece-linear function that specifies a path for the Carousel's items.

data.name: CarouselPanelFirstVisibleItemIndex
data.value: Gets or sets the index of the first visible item.

data.name: CarouselPanelAttractorPointIndex
data.value: Specifies the active element's position within the Carousel.

data.name: CarouselPanelActiveItemIndex
data.value: Gets or sets the active item by its index.

data.name: CarouselPanelActiveItem
data.value: Gets or sets the active item.

data.name: CarouselPanelAnimationDisabled
data.value: Specifies whether animation effects for item transitions are enabled.

data.name: CarouselPanelPathVisible
data.value: Gets or sets whether the control draws a line indicating the item path.

data.name: CarouselPanelActivateItemOnClick
data.value: Gets or sets whether clicking an item will activate it (move it to the Carousel's attractor point).

data.name: CarouselPanelIsRepeat
data.value: Gets or sets whether carousel scrolling is limited by the first and last item.

data.name: CarouselPanelSnapItemsToDevicePixels
data.value: Gets or sets whether items are rendered in accordance to device pixels.

data.name: CarouselPanelPathSizingMode
data.value: Gets or sets how the specified path should be resized when resizing the control.

data.name: CarouselPanelIsInvertedDirection
data.value: Gets or sets whether items move forward or backward along the specified path.

data.name: CarouselPanelPathPadding
data.value: Specifies the path's padding within the control's boundaries.

data.name: CarouselPanelIsAutoSizeItem
data.value: Gets or sets whether carousel items are automatically resized when changing the control's size.

data.name: CarouselPanelItemSize
data.value: Specifies the initial item size.

data.name: CarouselItemsControlCarousel
data.value: For internal use.

data.name: CarouselNavigatorCarousel
data.value: Specifies the CarouselPanel controlled by this navigator.

data.name: ParameterName
data.value: Gets or sets the parameter name.

data.name: ParameterAnimationMulFunction
data.value: Specifies a function that affects the parameter value while items are moving from one static position to another.

data.name: ParameterAnimationAddFunction
data.value: Specifies a function that affects the parameter value while items are moving from one static position to another.

data.name: ParameterDistributionFunction
data.value: Specifies the function that affects the parameter value along the entire item movement path.

data.name: ParameterInvertDistortionOnReverse
data.value: For internal use.
